From: Erik Bitzek <e.bitzek@mpie.de>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 20:58:12 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/5] Add compute sites/voronoi: Voronoi-vertex site catalogue

Vertices of the voro++ tessellation of all group atoms = centers of
largest empty spheres. Per-rank extraction with ghost halo, rmerge
single-linkage clustering (centroid, min clearance), deterministic
ownership tie-break (1e-9 box nudge) for sites exactly on periodic/
subdomain faces, criteria: clearance window (equal-var capable),
region, coordination (hostgroup), occcut/exclgroup veto, optional
probe Voronoi volume via compute_ghost_cell. Local array
x y z clearance [volume] coord + global scalar site count.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
